  "texts": [
    "This aligns with SDG 8, which aims to promote sustained, inclusive, and sustainable economic growth; full and productive employment; and decent work for all.",
    "Highlighting growth in green bond markets within African economic hubs such as Kenya, Nigeria, and South Africa, this study identifies opportunities for further expansion across the continent via this emerging climate finance mechanism.",
    "Moreover, fostering green bond markets also supports SDG 15, which seeks to protect, restore, and promote the sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems.",
    "However, critical gaps are revealed in fostering public-private partnerships, developing integrated policies and building effective institutional frameworks.",
    "Addressing these barriers through concerted efforts represents a key research avenue to unlock the impact of fully sustainable green bond development for climate-vulnerable African countries."
